org.jooq
Interface Store<T>

All Known Subinterfaces:
ArrayRecord<T>, Record, TableRecord<R>, UDTRecord<R>, UpdatableRecord<R>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayRecordImpl, RecordImpl, TableRecordImpl, UDTRecordImpl, UpdatableRecordImpl
public interface Store<T>

A common base type for Store and ArrayStore providing common, index-based functionality for storage objects

Author:
Lukas Eder
